Name: Gateway
Description: Special building. A Space Rift can be turned on at the target point and warp a time-limit special troop. Space Rift skills are also located on the top bar.

$Commands.Tooltip: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
$Commands.Name: Cancel

$Commands.Tooltip: Cancels construction of this structure, destroying the structure and giving a partial refund.
$Commands.Name: Cancel

$Commands.Tooltip: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
$Commands.Name: Cancel

$Commands.Tooltip: Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
$Commands.Name: Set Rally Point

$Commands.Tooltip:
Turn on Warp-in Authorizing for Artanis' Zealot, so that all Nexus Gateways can release four Zealots from the Space Rift.The Zealot can use Charge and Whirlwind.

Can attack the ground.
$Commands.Name: Warp-in Authorizing: Zealot

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing of Artanis' Zealot and make Space Rift stop warping Zealot.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: Zealot

$Commands.Tooltip: Nexus Gateway Can create a space rift at target location through Spear of Adun, and the rift can be destroyed by enemy units. After 10 seconds, rift will warp in massive support forces. Each category of units are allowed to be warped will increase Space Rift's resources cost and cooldown.
$Commands.Name: Space Rift

$Commands.Tooltip:
Turn on Warp-in Authorizing for Fenix's Instigator, so that all Nexus Gateways can release two Instigators from the Space Rift.The Instigator can automatically and continuously release Blink.

Can attack the ground and air.
$Commands.Name: Warp-in Authorizing: Instigator

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing of Fenix's Instigator and make Space Rift stop warping Invigorator.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: Instigator

$Commands.Tooltip:
Turn on Warp-in Authorizing for Alarak's Vanguard, so that all Nexus Gateways can release an Vanguard from the Space Rift. Immortal Taldarim attacks can cause AOE damage.

Can attack the ground and air.
$Commands.Name: Warp-in Authorizing: Vanguard

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing of Alarak's Vanguard and make Space Rift stop warping Vanguard.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: Vanguard

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing of Vorazun's Dark Templar, making Space Rift stop warping Dark Templar.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: Dark Templar

$Commands.Tooltip:
Turn on Warp-in Authorizing for Karax's Energizer, so that all Nexus Gateways can release two Energizers from the Space Rift.The Energizer can use Chrono Beam.

Can attack the ground and air.
$Commands.Name: Warp-in Authorizing: Energizer

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing of Karax's Energizer and make Space Rift stop warping Energizer.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: Energizer

$Commands.Tooltip:
Turn on Warp-in Authorizing for Rohana's High Templar, so that all Nexus Gateways can warp a High Templar after releasing Space Rift. High Templar can use Psi Storm.

Can attack the ground and air.
$Commands.Name: Warp-in Authorizing: High Templar

$Commands.Tooltip: Turn off Warp-in Authorizing for Rohana's High Templar, making Space Rift stop warp High Templar.
$Commands.Name: Inhibit Warp: High Templar

$Commands.Tooltip:
Nerazim Faction
Deadly warrior-assassin. Permanently cloaked. Can use Shadow Fury.**Can attack ground units**
$Commands.Name: Warp in Dark Templar
